t she heard the screams of a woman, rather than an anguished man, on the night of Steenkamp’s death.</b></p><p><b>• Burger rejected defence claims that the loud noises she heard coming from Pistorius’s house were the sound of him using a cricket bat to smash down the door of the bathroom. </b>She said she heard four loud gunshots, and that the intervals between each were too short for the noises to have been a bat swung against a wooden door.</p><p><b>• Burger disputed claims that she used her husband’s witness statement as a template for her own - and denied basing her evidence on “retrospective knowledge” gleaned from later media coverage.</b></p><p><b>• The defence also sought to question Burger’s evidence by arguing  that Steenkamp would have been too severely injured by gunshots to have been able to scream.</b></p><p><b>• Another neighbour, </b><b>Estelle van der Merwe, told the court she woke to hear an argument and four noises - which could have been consecutive gunshots - on the night Steenkamp died. <br></b></p><p><b>• The judge has reminded the media not to publish any images of witnesses after a TV channel and several papers carried a still photograph of one witness</b>.</p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T14:36:23.904Z\">at 2.36pm GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315cdf0e4b093d4729c31c6\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T13:00:32.124Z\">1.00pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>The judge agrees to Nel’s request that the case be adjourned for the day, reminds Johnson that he is still under oath, and rises. The court will sit again tomorrow at 9.30am (7.30am UK time).<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315cd8fe4b0149dfe8e3a92\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:56:49.211Z\">12.56pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440832498663059456\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;We listened to court proceedings on the radio.&quot; It was said only one person shouted that night. &quot;Our version differed from that.&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440832498663059456\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315cc9ce4b0984a90a9e105\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:56:34.724Z\">12.56pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Johnson said he realised that he and his wife had been far closer to the crime scene than other witnesses, but decided to contact a lawyer rather than go straight to the police as they wanted to keep out of the public eye.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440831863238578176\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;On TV I saw an aerial photo of the Silverwoods estate. I was surprised to see how close we are to the house where it happened.&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440831863238578176\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440832237097869312\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;As the bail application proceeded... we realised there were no other witnesses who had come forward closer to us.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440832237097869312\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:57:54.439Z\">at 12.57pm GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315cb27e4b093d4729c31c0\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:50:01.707Z\">12.50pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Johnson said he was surprised to be told that Pistorius had shot his girlfriend as he had assumed he had heard a break-in the previous night. <br></p><p>He said he found it hard to square that account with what he had witnessed, as he had heard both a man and a woman calling for help, and assumed they were reacting to an armed burglary and not having a domestic dispute.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440831332206125056\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: We heard a male and female voice. We thought maybe the attackers had gone and left a husband and wife tied up. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440831332206125056\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c994e4b0149dfe8e3a8d\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:42:38.854Z\">12.42pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Johnson says he heard shots and later found out there had been a total of four. Asked about the timings of the shots, he says: “There was a small pause after the first shot and the remaining shots were fired in close succession.” He and his wife were shocked, and she told him she feared the man whose voice they had heard had been shot dead in front of his wife.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440828710476722176\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;I remember during the succession of shots I heard a lady scream again, and shortly after the last shot.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440828710476722176\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440829477187096576\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;We were under the impression someone had been attacked in their house in a very secure complex.&quot; Didn&#39;t want same to happen to us.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440829477187096576\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c808e4b0984a90a9e0f6\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:38:42.615Z\">12.38pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Johnson says he could hear the voice of a woman “[who] was in trouble. It was clearly distressed calls”. Then he heard a man call, “Help! Help!”. He rang estate security on his wife’s phone and told them that people were being attacked in the neighbouring estate. It turned out that the number in her phone was for the security office for the estate where they used to live. He told them he had got the wrong number and went back to the balcony.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440827993976344576\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: At that point we were under impression the house was being attacked so I wanted to bring it to attention of security. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440827993976344576\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c754e4b0149dfe8e3a88\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:30:14.466Z\">12.30pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440826327415783425\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson: &quot;I lifted my head to make sure I heard correctly. After I jumped out of bed I went out on to the balcony.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440826327415783425\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c728e4b0da1677ed2d18\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:29:33.515Z\">12.29pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440826052470792192\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Johnson, softly spoken: It was a normal evening, we went to bed between 9 and 10. I was woken in the early hours by screams. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440826052470792192\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c5bce4b0984a90a9e0f0\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:27:40.504Z\">12.27pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Van der Merwe has finished her evidence. The next witness is Charl Johnson, husband of the first witness, Michelle Burger, who comes back into court to watch. <br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c537e4b0da1677ed2d15\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:22:36.225Z\">12.22pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>We’re back to the question of whether it was a man’s voice or woman’s voice that was heard that night. Van der Merwe says it was a woman’s.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440823854999416832\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Van der Merwe: &quot;A woman&#39;s voice is higher than a man&#39;s voice. A man&#39;s voice is more like a bass.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440823854999416832\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c287e4b0149dfe8e3a80\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:10:34.963Z\">12.10pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440821209488306176\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: &quot;You did not tell your husband those gunshot sounds followed an argument.&quot; Van der Merwe: &quot;No, I did not.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440821209488306176\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c20fe4b093d4729c31b8\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:08:39.995Z\">12.08pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Van der Merwe says she knows a woman’s voice when she hears it - especially if that woman is angry.<br></p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:23:50.570Z\">at 12.23pm GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c1efe4b0149dfe8e3a7f\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:07:14.627Z\">12.07pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440820571354316800\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Van der Merwe: &quot;I had no idea where the voice was coming from... I was scared to walk around the other side of the building.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440820571354316800\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315c0eae4b0da1677ed2d0b\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:03:16.391Z\">12.03pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440819200316030976\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux tells van der Merwe why she heard noises in February this year. &quot;We did tests of a man and woman screaming as loud as they can in...&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440819200316030976\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440819276807544832\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>&quot;the bedroom to determine how far sound would travel at 2 to 3 in the morning. What&#39;s interesting is that you could not hear the screaming.&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440819276807544832\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315bfcae4b0984a90a9e0eb\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T12:01:44.793Z\">12.01pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Proceedings have resumed. <br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440818932396478465\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Judge Masipa enters court but <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> is missing and has to be fetched. Nel begins as <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> family members scurry to their seats.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440818932396478465\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315bd9ee4b0149dfe8e3a7e\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T11:49:35.967Z\">11.49am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2014/mar/04/oscar-pistorius-trial-neighbour-lawyer-video\">Here</a>’s a video of Roux questioning Pistorius’s former neighbour Michelle Burger</p> <figure class=\"element element-video\" data-canonical-url=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2014/mar/04/oscar-pistorius-trial-neighbour-lawyer-video\"                        data-show-ads=\"true\"                data-video-id=\"2053580\"                data-video-name=\"Oscar Pistorius trial: neighbour questioned by defence lawyer – video\"                data-video-provider=\"Reuters\"                data-video-poster=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2014/3/4/1393930761853/Oscar-Pistorius-002.jpg\"> <video data-media-id=\"gu-video-431250698\" class=\"gu-video\" controls=\"controls\" poster=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/audio/video/2014/3/4/1393930761853/Oscar-Pistorius-002.jpg\"> <source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/mainwebsite/2014/03/04/140304pistoriusDay2-16x9.mp4\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/3gp/large/2014/03/04/140304pistoriusDay2_3gpLg16x9.3gp\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/webM/2014/03/04//140304pistoriusDay2.webm\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/HLS/2014/03/04/140304pistoriusDay2/140304pistoriusDay2.m3u8\"></source><source src=\"http://cdn.theguardian.tv/3gp/small/2014/03/04/140304pistoriusDay2_3gpSml16x9.3gp\"></source> </video> <figcaption>The defence lawyer for Olympic and Paralympic athlete Oscar Pistorius questions the credibility of a key witness, neighbour Michelle Burger Duration: 3 mins 3 secs</figcaption> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T11:55:23.038Z\">at 11.55am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315b229e4b093d4729c31a2\" class=\"block is-summary\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T11:09:29.437Z\">11.09am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <h2 class=\"block-title\">Summary</h2> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>On the second day of the Pistorius trial:</p><p><b>• Michelle Burger, a neighbour of the athlete, has again insisted that she heard the screams of a woman, rather than an anguished man, on the night of Steenkamp’s death.</b></p><p><b>• Burger has rejected defence claims that the loud noises she heard coming from Pistorius’s house were the sound of him using a cricket bat to smash down the door of the bathroom. She says she heard four loud gunshots, and that the intervals between each were too short for the noises to have been a bat swung against a wooden door.</b></p><p><b>• Burger has disputed claims that she used her husband’s witness statement as a template for her own - and denied basing her evidence on “retrospective knowledge” gleaned from later media coverage.</b></p><p><b>• The defence has sought to question Burger’s evidence by arguing  that Steenkamp would have been too severely injured to have been able to scream after being shot.<br></b></p><p><b>• Another neighbour, </b><b>Estelle van der Merwe, has told the court she woke to hear an argument and four noises - which could have been consecutive gunshots - on the night Steenkamp died.<br></b></p><p><b>• The judge has reminded the media not to publish any images of witnesses after a TV channel and several papers carried a still photograph of one witness</b>.<br></p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T13:30:37.384Z\">at 1.30pm GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315b00fe4b0984a90a9e0d9\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:51:06.657Z\">10.51am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>The court has risen for an early lunch. Nel will resume his questioning of Van der Merwe this afternoon.<br></p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:53:02.666Z\">at 10.53am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315ae5ae4b0984a90a9e0d7\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:43:40.246Z\">10.43am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440801427066085376\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Van der Merwe: &quot;It seemed like two people but I couldn&#39;t hear the other person&#39;s voice.&quot; I didn&#39;t know where it was coming from. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440801427066085376\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:52:25.615Z\">at 10.52am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315ac20e4b0da1677ed2cef\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:36:17.065Z\">10.36am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>On hearing the “shots”, Van der Merwe turned her husband, who told her that the noises were gunshots. He looked out of the window, but could see nothing. They went back to bed and her husband called security. Shortly after, she heard someone “crying out loud”.<br></p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:45:32.191Z\">at 10.45am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315abebe4b0da1677ed2cec\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:33:53.591Z\">10.33am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Van der Merwe says the four “shots” were consecutive.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440796771959070721\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Van der Merwe: &quot;You want me to describe the sounds? Bang, bang. That&#39;s the best I can do.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440796771959070721\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315aa33e4b0149dfe8e3a69\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:33:00.917Z\">10.33am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Van der Merwe says she, her husband and son went to bed around nine. She says he woke up at 1.56am to hear people talking in loud voices, as if fighting. It lasted about an hour but she could not hear what they said, nor determine what language they were speaking. <br></p><p>She says she was annoyed by the disturbance as her son had an exam the next day. She put a pillow over her head to block out the noise and tried to go back to sleep. Later, she tried to see what she could see, but, failing to make out anything, went back to sleep. She says she was woken around 3am by four “noises”. Interpreter translates “noises” as gunshots but, once again, the lawyers step in to question the accuracy of the interpreting.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315aa0be4b0da1677ed2ce8\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:25:16.536Z\">10.25am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794896866095104\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Van der Merwe says she did not know <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> and had never met him.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794896866095104\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a9e8e4b0149dfe8e3a68\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:24:43.506Z\">10.24am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794747938959360\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Second witness is Estelle van der Merwe, another neighbour of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a>.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794747938959360\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a93be4b0149dfe8e3a67\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:22:14.917Z\">10.22am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Judge tells Burger she may leave the witness box and thanks her for her evidence.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794235277549568\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Masipa: &quot;Mrs Burger, thank you very much for your assistance, you may step down.&quot; She leaves looking upset; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> does not watch her.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440794235277549568\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:23:07.544Z\">at 10.23am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a342e4b093d4729c318f\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:20:45.483Z\">10.20am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"gu-fc-625a5624-e702-4139-a797-67b2f4b9078c\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/4/1393926976805/9ea60ef8-786d-4f89-bb41-9ae58140e3c1-460x307.jpeg\" alt=\"Journalists at work during a break in the Oscar Pistorius trial\" width=\"460\" height=\"307\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption>Journalists at work during a break in the Oscar Pistorius trial. <br>Photograph: Kim Ludbrook/AFP/Getty Images</figcaption> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a834e4b093d4729c319b\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:20:39.621Z\">10.20am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Nel now re-examining Burger and asks if the sequence of shots (one shot, a long  pause and then three more shots, far closer together) could have fitted with a cricket bat being used to smash a door. Burger says she thinks too much time would have elapsed between cricket bat blows for a bat to have made the noises she heard.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440793432882024448\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger breaks down, wipes tears from her eyes with a tissue. Nel says he also wants to get her out of here. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440793432882024448\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:22:41.225Z\">at 10.22am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a7e7e4b093d4729c3198\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:16:55.306Z\">10.16am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux has wrapped up his cross-examination by questioning whether Burger is able to recognise the sound of a gunshot as she has not heard a gun fired for some year. <br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a712e4b0149dfe8e3a62\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:13:55.638Z\">10.13am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791825574400001\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: I put it to you that made up your mind not to believe his version and interpreted cricket bat as gunshots, his cries as her screams.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791825574400001\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <p>Burger says, once again, that gunshots make far more noise than a cricket bat would on a wooden door.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a670e4b0149dfe8e3a60\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:10:43.589Z\">10.10am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Burger insists she heard a woman scream following, or overlapping with, the last of four shots.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791016853880833\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux questions the timing of woman&#39;s final scream. Burger replies: &quot;I wasn&#39;t there with a stopwatch.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791016853880833\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791267153162240\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;The emotions I heard were very intense.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440791267153162240\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:11:09.332Z\">at 10.11am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a5f8e4b093d4729c3196\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:09:37.897Z\">10.09am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux replies that the medical evidence shows that Steenkamp could not have screamed after being shot as she would have lost “cognitive function”.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440790684774068225\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> is bent double, hands behind his head, as Roux describes bullets hitting Steenkamp&#39;s head causing &quot;brain damage&quot;.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440790684774068225\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440790883860873216\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> uses white handkerchief to wipe tears from his eyes.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440790883860873216\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a5afe4b093d4729c3194\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:07:37.332Z\">10.07am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Nel objects to Roux’s use of the ballistic evidence and suggests that his opponent’s cross-examination is again relying on selective quotation.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a4a1e4b0984a90a9e0cc\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:05:54.891Z\">10.05am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux is now sketching out Pistorius’s attempts to smash the bathroom door with a cricket bat: “It was a stage of heightened anxiety; it was a pinnacle … It was him screaming, absolutely anxious.” <br></p><p>Roux suggests what Burger heard were not Steenkamp’s screams, but the cries of his deeply upset client. He also says that ballistic evidence shows that Steenkamp would by then have been too seriously wounded by the gunshot to her head to have screamed out.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a461e4b093d4729c3191\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:01:07.978Z\">10.01am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788876685111296\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: &quot;You will even go so far, ma&#39;am, as to call it a mockery rather than make any concession that will help this man.&quot; Nel objects.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788876685111296\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a429e4b0149dfe8e3a5c\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T10:00:41.482Z\">10.00am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Again, Burger suggests that Roux would be better off asking Pistorius these questions.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a373e4b0984a90a9e0cb\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:59:06.478Z\">9.59am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux asks Burger to be objective. If a man is about to shoot his girlfriend who is hiding in a bathroom, is it not “inconsistent” that he would shout for help, he asks? Burger replies that the man’s cries were “part of the sequence” of the events of that night.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788219517366273\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;She shouted for help. He shouted for help. I don&#39;t know why.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788219517366273\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788408172945408\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux to Burger: To me it&#39;s obvious you will not make a concession &quot;because you think it will be good&quot; for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a>.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440788408172945408\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:59:37.022Z\">at 9.59am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a2e6e4b0149dfe8e3a59\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:54:53.245Z\">9.54am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"gu-fc-b88c7cb9-a5bc-4a0b-9402-6b7528998a7b\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/4/1393926881280/60246511-ed6d-421d-8108-4839797d6f24-460x276.jpeg\" alt=\"Oscar Pistorius talks with his defence team during a break in proceedings.\" width=\"460\" height=\"276\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption>Oscar Pistorius talks with his defence team during a break in proceedings. Photograph: Antoine de Ras/EPA</figcaption> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a23ee4b093d4729c318d\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:53:10.369Z\">9.53am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux has returned to yesterday’s questions about how Burger could have told the difference between a gunshot and the sound of a cricket back struck against a wooden bathroom door, and between a female voice and an anguished male voice.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440786412657324032\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;I really can&#39;t see that a bat and a gunshot sound the same.&quot; If I hit a bat and pulled a trigger in court, one would be louder.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440786412657324032\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:54:39.176Z\">at 9.54am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a16fe4b0984a90a9e0c8\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:51:07.585Z\">9.51am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Burger on the similarities between the statements: <br></p><blockquote class=\"quoted\"><p>My lady, that’s what I heard and I’m glad that my husband heard exactly the same.<br></p></blockquote><p>She again denies using her husband’s testimony as the basis of her own.<br></p><p>Roux is reprimanded by the judge - and apologises - after replying, sarcastically,  that “of course” Burger hadn’t read her husband’s statement.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5315a064e4b0da1677ed2cdc\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:46:11.429Z\">9.46am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux says the similarities between the two statements are “striking”. Burger says it’s because they both follow the same sequence of events, as elicited by police questioning. “I answered on the questions asked,” she says, adding that they were both asked the same questions by the investigating officer. Burger denies using her husband’s statement as a template for her own.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440784563766173696\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: &quot;You don&#39;t need extra qualifications to see the striking similarities&quot; between Burger and husband&#39;s statements. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440784563766173696\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440784954692104193\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: Police captain asked us about the sequence of events. &quot;The sequence was the same as my husband&#39;s sequence.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440784954692104193\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:46:38.097Z\">at 9.46am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-53159fd7e4b0da1677ed2cda\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:43:03.504Z\">9.43am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Laughter erupts in court after Burger tells Roux her statement describing the open windows of her bedroom that night was very similar to her husband’s description “because we were in the same bedroom”.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53159f0fe4b093d4729c3188\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:38:49.680Z\">9.38am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux says he will go through the statements, side-by-side, to highlight the similarities. “It’s as if the one were used predominantly as a template for the other,” he says.<br></p> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:39:52.567Z\">at 9.39am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-53159e76e4b0984a90a9e0c5\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:37:12.301Z\">9.37am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Proceedings have resumed. The judge and two assessors are being handed copies of Michelle Burger’s husband’s witness statement, which, says Roux, is “remarkably similar … too similar” to her own.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53159636e4b0149dfe8e3a4a\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T09:00:57.465Z\">9.00am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>The court has now adjourned for a short break.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-531594b4e4b0149dfe8e3a48\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:54:19.426Z\">8.54am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440771796560650240\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux to Burger: You didn&#39;t hear screams while calling security? &quot;Why is it necessary that I have to put the same question four times?&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440771796560650240\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53159322e4b093d4729c317e\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:50:08.628Z\">8.50am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Roux asks how, from a distance of 177m, Burger could have heard emotional screams and shouts from a locked, enclosed bathroom. He invites the court to visit the crime scene and judge for themselves how hard it would be to hear noises from Pistorius’s bathroom from Burger’s house. He says it’s impossible; Burger points out a lot of construction has taken place since the killing of Steenkamp, making it harder to hear noise from neighbouring properties.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440770230558531584\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: We know that when the shots were fired Reeva was in the toilet, the door was closed and locked, the window was closed. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440770230558531584\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440770766150193152\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: We will go and test whether you can hear a scream from there. Burger: There are new houses in the way that weren&#39;t there at the time.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440770766150193152\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:50:33.484Z\">at 8.50am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-531592a3e4b0149dfe8e3a46\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:46:34.000Z\">8.46am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Burger says she could hear the noises from Pistorius’s house as they are no buildings between her house and his. She adds that she had her bedroom windows open and did not have a fan on.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440769461914591232\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: There was screaming &quot;moments&quot; before the first shot, then scream during the four shots, then last scream just after. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440769461914591232\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440769837413838848\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: &quot;You had the ability from 177 metres to hear emotion and fear and growing intensity?&quot; Burger: Our windows were open, we had no air con</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440769837413838848\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:47:04.815Z\">at 8.47am GMT</time></p> </div> <div id=\"block-53159216e4b093d4729c317d\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-04T08:43:03.891Z\">8.43am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440768561045192704\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;The last time I heard the woman&#39;s voice was shortly after the last shot.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440768561045192704\">March 4, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-531591f9e4b0149dfe8e3a44\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time