s.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53146fe9e4b093d4729c30d0\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T12:05:00.552Z\">12.05pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440457549779714048\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;My husband said it could be four, five or six gunshots. He is not sure.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440457549779714048\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53146f7ae4b093d4729c30cf\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T12:03:09.937Z\">12.03pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440457028637454337\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Roux: &quot;Why could it not be the cricket bat you heard bashing the door?&quot; Burger: &quot;I clearly heard four gunshots.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a></p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440457028637454337\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53146f0de4b0149dfe8e399f\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T12:01:18.501Z\">12.01pm <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440456638411988992\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Burger: &quot;I don&#39;t understand how Mr <a href=\"https: