.455Z\">9.55am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440424718043062272\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a>: The state has conceded it can no longer establish that I had my prosthetics on at the time of the shooting.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440424718043062272\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53145134e4b093d4729c30aa\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T09:54:00.384Z\">9.54am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440424180907929601\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> says witness&#39;s house is 105 metres from his and it would not have been possible for witness to hear voices raised in argument.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440424180907929601\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-531450c0e4b093d4729c30a9\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T09:53:39.050Z\">9.53am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Pistorius says he cannot understand how the prosecution can allege that he and Steenkamp had argued before her death, nor its allegation that “I shot her because of the argument”. Denies there was an argument.<br></p> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-5314504be4b0149dfe8e3982\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T09:50:45.939Z\">9.50am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <p>Pistorius denies prosecution suggestions that he “pursued” Steenkamp to the bathroom.<br></p> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440423552156590080\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a>: The state has embarked on a strategy based on &quot;unsubstantiated allegations&quot; to argue that I murdered Reeva, as in bail hearing.</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440423552156590080\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53144fd1e4b0da1677ed2c04\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T09:48:03.625Z\">9.48am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440423186232909825\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a>: &quot;I approached the bathroom armed with my firearm so I could defend Reeva and I. I believed Reeva was still in bed.&quot;</p>&mdash; David Smith (@SmithInAfrica) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440423186232909825\">March 3, 2014</a></blockquote> </figure> </div> </div> <div id=\"block-53144fa5e4b093d4729c30a5\" class=\"block\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2014-03-03T09:47:22.173Z\">9.47am <span class=\"timezone\">GMT</span></time> </p> <div class=\"block-elements\"> <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SmithInAfrica/statuses/440422938102087680\"> <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Pistorius&amp;src=hash\">#Pistorius</a> stateme